Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.46,0:01:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyways, pros have to play\Ngames, right!? Games!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.63,0:01:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,When do I get to play Touya!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.42,0:01:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know, Waya?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.68,0:01:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.93,0:01:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But I am connected!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,To Touya, and to Touya's dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.63,0:01:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the same world already!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.35,0:01:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be playing them someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.05,0:02:00.85,Sai,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.27,0:02:04.06,Sai,,0,0,0,,I'm not the one that's connected...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.57,0:02:06.32,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.52,0:02:08.52,Sai,,0,0,0,,It's just Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.82,0:02:14.78,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs15\t(1977,2937,1,\fs25)\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord1\shad0\frz21\move(462,173,536,8,2022,2937)}Ochi Kousuke (13)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.82,0:02:14.78,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs15\t(1977,2937,1,\fs25)\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord1\shad0\frz24\pos(352,402)}Shindou Hikaru (14)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.82,0:02:14.78,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs15\t(1977,2937,1,\fs25)\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord1\shad0\frz24\move(525,324,634,270,1977,2937)}Waya Yoshitaka (15)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:11.53,Background,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That boy passed...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.03,0:02:14.50,Background,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I see, his name is Shindou.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.20,0:02:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He may be part of the new wave\Nthat Ogata was speaking of.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.83,0:02:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear that, Sai!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.33,0:02:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be playing Touya Meijin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.96,0:02:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember the new first dan series!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.27,0:02:27.11,Sai,,0,0,0,,Let me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.93,0:02:29.34,Sai,,0,0,0,,Let me play, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:34.34,Title_eps_top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(316,0)\fscx197\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\blur0.8\pos(355,115)}The Forty-Seventh Match
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:34.34,Title_eps,,0,0,0,,{\fad(274,0)\q2\blur0.8\fscy70\fscx333\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\pos(325,365)}Sai vs. Meijin
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.31,0:02:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,S... Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.74,0:02:47.58,Sai,,0,0,0,,Let me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:50.96,Sai,,0,0,0,,Please let me play, Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya's going to be watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.31,0:03:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be just Touya either,\NWaya and Ochi will be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:12.52,Background,,0,0,0,,And it will be on Weekly Go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.93,0:03:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And... there is a reverse komi of\N5.5 in the new first dan series.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The new first dan is at an advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.23,0:03:29.00,Background,,0,0,0,,You're going to win for sure if I let you play it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.41,0:03:31.61,Background,,0,0,0,,I know how strong you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.59,0:03:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... going to be hidden in your shadow again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:38.53,Sai,,0,0,0,,Then hide in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You think it won't matter to me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.83,0:03:46.41,Sai,,0,0,0,,Then, when exactly are you going to let me play!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:04:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Sai? You said so yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:04.72,Background,,0,0,0,,That you have an infinite amount of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:06.72,Background,,0,0,0,,So you're not in a hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.24,0:04:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That even if I died, you'd just wait\Nfor the next person to possess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:17.82,Background,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.54,0:04:22.64,Sai,,0,0,0,,I... think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.05,0:04:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,See!? If I'm the second, then there\Nis going to be a third and a fourth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.54,0:04:30.53,Sai,,0,0,0,,You don't understand, Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.38,0:04:33.28,Sai,,0,0,0,,I've been worried lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:36.09,Sai,,0,0,0,,about how long I can remain in the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're just worrying about nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, I'm tired of getting in trouble\Nevery time I let you play.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.11,0:04:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask the third guy you possess to let you play.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:49.69,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.11,0:04:53.96,Sai,,0,0,0,,Is Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:58.04,Sai,,0,0,0,,Not going to let me play anymore?
