Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:40.51,Background,,0,0,0,,Master Kuwabara.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my, if it isn't Ogata-kun. It has been awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't met face to face since\Nthe Honinbou Match, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:06:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that seven game match fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.01,0:06:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned a lot during that match.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.98,0:06:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you've been doing well lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you completely defeat Kurata-kun\Njust the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And you, master, seem to\Nbe doing poorly as of late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.78,0:06:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm too old, I don't want much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.74,0:06:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I won't give the title\Nof Honinbou to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And, why is Kuwabara Honinbou here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Try these, Ogata-kun, instead of\Nsucking on that candy of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I here, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.94,0:07:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll turn that question right back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.93,0:07:04.95,Background,,0,0,0,,It's only a new first dan playing today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:11.65,Background,,0,0,0,,Even if the Meijin is playing, it's not something\Nthat someone like you would come watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means that this boy is part of the new\Nwave that is coming to the Go world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.52,0:07:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You know Shindou?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw him play somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, I was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.35,0:07:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew he was exceptional when I saw\Nhim. My sixth sense is still sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.15,0:07:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sixth sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The sixth sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.98,0:07:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I merely passed by Shindou once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.43,0:07:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You just passed him by?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.53,0:07:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.82,0:07:46.36,Background,,0,0,0,,Shindou is going first, and Ochi you're\Nplaying next week. That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:48.59,Background,,0,0,0,,Waya, have they notified you yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:49.41,Background,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:52.47,Background,,0,0,0,,Oh man, I want to play already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.25,0:08:00.52,Thinking,,0,0,0,,O-Ogata 9-dan and Kuwabara Honinbou!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.63,0:08:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's sit over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why are two top pros here to\Nwatch a new first dan match?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably because they are interested in Shindou.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogata-san was watching Shindou\Nduring the Wakajishisen, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.28,0:08:30.16,Background,,0,0,0,,He even invited Shindou to\Nthe Meijin's study sessions!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,To the Meijin's study sessions!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, he did refuse the invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.58,0:08:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He was on his way to my master's study session.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know about Master Kuwabara though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.19,0:08:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Master Kuwabara\Nhas his eye on Shindou, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:54.22,Background,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:09:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogata-san... and Master Kuwabara?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.36,0:09:02.63,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He's here after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.62,0:09:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ochi-kun, good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.03,0:09:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You know Touya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the Meijin's son, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Nice to meet you, I'm Touya Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're someone else that's interested in Shindou?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.80,0:09:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.66,0:09:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, I see. Then the Meijin must be, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the Meijin, who has five titles, is interested\Nin that boy. How interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.74,0:09:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Kuwabara...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.53,0:09:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Just who is Shindou?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He passed with us, he's our rival... and our friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:50.07,Background,,0,0,0,,Okay, say cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.07,0:10:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira is here to watch today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.87,0:10:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew that Akira was concerned about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.04,0:10:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Akira wasn't the only one, Ogata-kun\Nand I felt the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.82,0:10:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I requested to play you for this match today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.46,0:10:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:48.13,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Room of Deep Contemplation... I'm going to be playing\Nin this room, that Waya and I looked at last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.25,0:11:21.23,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:28.15,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:47.63,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.67,0:12:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:12.65,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai! Get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:23.27,Background,,0,0,0,,Say... Ogata-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:25.77,Background,,0,0,0,,This match...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to bet on who wins?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.65,0:12:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Bet? Interesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.11,0:12:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.57,0:12:36.32,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Bet!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.76,0:12:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a reverse komi of 5.5.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.79,0:12:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But it will still be difficult against Touya Kouyou.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But not if the Meijin lets the boy win.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.22,0:12:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.73,0:12:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that man wouldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.84,0:12:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And? Who are you going to bet on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.15,0:13:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Going against the odds?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.90,0:13:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. I don't gamble to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.31,0:13:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't. Or what is it? Did you\Nwant to bet on the boy, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Having studied under the Meijin,\NI have faith that he will win.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Just who is Shindou?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He passed with us... he's our rival... and our friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:41.60,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Shindou!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.77,0:13:48.06,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HC5FEC1&}Shindou is going to play my father under the\Nscrutiny of Ogata-san and Master Kuwabara.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.31,0:13:51.01,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He has finally come this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.19,0:13:54.35,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting.. for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.32,0:13:57.57,Thinking,,0,0,0,,What kind of game is he going to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:14:00.97,Thinking,,0,0,0,,What kind of game is he going to show me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.69,0:14:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:27.60,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.43,0:14:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Shindou-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:46.36,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:51.05,Sai,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Hikaru... I just wanted\Nto sit here for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.81,0:14:52.71,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.41,0:15:24.63,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Idiot. You didn't need to sulk now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.99,0:15:26.74,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'm about to play a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.16,0:15:30.08,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I understand how you feel, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:31.64,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:33.83,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:36.72,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:39.19,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:46.71,Thinking,,0,0,0,,There aren't going to be many chances like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.23,0:15:58.55,Thinking,,0,0,0,,No! No! If I let Sai play with the advantage\Nof a 5.5 reverse komi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:16:01.04,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He's going to win for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:04.84,Thinking,,0,0,0,,And I'll become the center of attention...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:08.53,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.95,0:16:10.74,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.58,0:16:13.68,Thinking,,0,0,0,,A handicap...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:17.45,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He'll play differently with a handicap...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:21.55,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Touya Meijin is giving a handicap\Nof the first move and 5.5 moku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.51,0:16:25.94,Thinking,,0,0,0,,If Sai were to take on more than that... like...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.91,0:16:32.59,Thinking,,0,0,0,,If Sai were to play with a handicap of 15 moku,\Nhe wouldn't be able to play normally...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:37.06,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Then they might not find out about Sai's strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.94,0:16:39.02,Sai,,0,0,0,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.57,0:16:41.98,Sai,,0,0,0,,I'll pretend that there's a 15\Nmoku gap to begin with!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.39,0:16:43.28,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.11,0:16:45.80,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Do you really get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.29,0:16:50.49,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Even if you do have the first move, you're\Ngoing to play a lot of unreasonable moves,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.49,0:16:52.03,Thinking,,0,0,0,,if there's a 15 moku gap on the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:54.13,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HC5FEC1&}You're playing against Touya's dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.38,0:16:56.12,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HC5FEC1&}He'll crush you, and that'll be the end of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.33,0:16:58.36,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HC5FEC1&}Do you really want to play a game like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It is time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The new first dan will play first. Komi\Nis a reverse komi of 5.5 moku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.16,0:17:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You have two hours each.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:10.80,Background,,0,0,0,,After you use all of your time you\Nwill have one minute per move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.18,0:17:14.12,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.70,0:17:20.82,Background,,0,0,0,,Then, please begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.73,0:17:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.07,0:17:27.79,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Okay. If you're okay with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.82,0:17:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:43.89,Thinking,,0,0,0,,What kind of a game are you going to play, Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:07.27,Background,,0,0,0,,It has been twenty minutes since the game started.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It has started... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.25,0:18:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He's really into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Into it, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.50,0:18:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If he isn't, then what is it? Do you think\Nhe's too nervous to pick up the stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.60,0:18:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what Shindou is thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.01,0:18:28.96,Background,,0,0,0,,He knew who his opponent was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.69,0:18:34.53,Background,,0,0,0,,One would usually decide his\Nfirst move ahead of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They only have two hours each for this match.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ridiculous to use twenty minutes of it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I'd never use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.91,0:18:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He's planning something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.29,0:18:57.27,Background,,0,0,0,,He is exceptional, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.93,0:19:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:18.22,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Shindou-kun..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.65,0:19:23.48,Sai,,0,0,0,,To win by more than 15 moku...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.37,0:19:27.01,Sai,,0,0,0,,I know how impossible that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:30.55,Sai,,0,0,0,,My opponent isn't merely someone from a Go salon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.63,0:19:36.45,Sai,,0,0,0,,He is probably someone who would fight\Nme to the last half moku in a real match.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.62,0:19:38.37,Sai,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.42,0:19:43.45,Sai,,0,0,0,,The atmosphere before the board\Nis the same as last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:47.92,Sai,,0,0,0,,No matter what the circumstances\Nare, you're finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:50.96,Sai,,0,0,0,,going to respond to each of my moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.09,0:19:56.73,Sai,,0,0,0,,To head for a win of more than 15 moku...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.63,0:20:00.86,Sai,,0,0,0,,I'll have to start a fight where one of us dies...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.34,0:20:04.64,Sai,,0,0,0,,Either he will get wiped out, or I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.69,0:20:07.96,Sai,,0,0,0,,How far will I be able to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.65,0:20:13.23,Sai,,0,0,0,,Upper right corner, Hoshi!
